his stick soloing
on <i>Black Dog.</i>

02:50.336 --> 02:52.072
You know,
like that first gig.

02:52.105 --> 02:55.041
I'm not jealous.
I'm really not.

02:55.075 --> 02:56.510
I'm glad I bombed
the audition,

02:56.543 --> 02:59.412
because, you know,
if I hadn't...

02:59.445 --> 03:01.782
