03:24.104 --> 03:25.572
You just kissed Nick!

03:25.606 --> 03:26.873
Yeah, so?

03:28.509 --> 03:30.276
Are you going out
with him?

03:30.310 --> 03:32.412
No... Well...

03:32.445 --> 03:34.515
We haven't gone
on a real date
or anything.

03:35.816 --> 03:37.083
It's just that...

03:37.117 --> 03:38.418
Well, we were hanging
out the other day,

03:38.451 --> 03:39.753
and he was
kinda depressed,

03:39.786 --> 03:41.121
and we kissed.

03:41.154 --> 03:42.756
