make it all better.

10:00.466 --> 10:01.968
SAM: You guys are jerks!

10:03.570 --> 10:06.439
Ohh! Hi, Cindy.

10:06.472 --> 10:08.174
Hi, Sam. Hey, Nate.

10:08.208 --> 10:09.275
It's Neal...

10:09.309 --> 10:10.811
OK, so, Bill,
I was thinking,

10:10.844 --> 10:13.547
we should probably
get started on
our lab assignment.

10:13.580 --> 10:16.550
I have cheerleading
practice at 3:00,

10:16.583 --> 10:19.553
French club at 3:45,

10:19.586 --> 10:21.421
but do you think you
could come over at, like...

10:21.454 --> 10:23.323
4:30?

10:23.356 --> 10:25.258
(CLEARS THROAT)
To your house?

10:25.291 --> 10:26.292
Mm‐hmm.

10:30.230 --> 10:32.198
I think... I think
I could squeeze you in.

10:32.232 --> 10:34.400
Great! I'll see you then.

10:34.434 --> 10:35.769
Bye, Sam.

10:37.771 --> 10:41.007
