or Old Spice?

10:45.445 --> 10:47.413
Definitely Old Spice.

10:49.883 --> 10:53.253
Ah, check it out.
Donkey basketball Saturday.

10:53.286 --> 10:54.521
I love those things.

10:54.555 --> 10:55.789
I think they're mean.

10:55.822 --> 10:58.659
Oh, yeah, like the donkeys
really give a care.

10:58.692 --> 11:00.360
Well, how would you
like some big fat teacher

11:00.393 --> 11:02.629
sitting on your back
while you had to run
around a gym?

11:02.663 --> 11:04.464
Yeah, how did
your date with
Fredricks go?

11:04.497 --> 11:06.199
Ooh!
(BELL RINGS)

11:07.634 --> 11:09.135
You want to hang out
Friday night?

11:09.570 --> 11:11.137
Um, yeah.

11:11.171 --> 11:12.706
Yeah? Cool!

11:12.739 --> 11:14.741
Well, have you seen
<i>The Elephant Man?</i>

11:16.076 --> 11:17.110
Hmm?

11:17.143 --> 11:18.144
The movie.

11:19.079 --> 11:21.347
Oh, ohh! The...

11:21.381 --> 11:22.516
Guy with...
The deformed guy.

11:22.549 --> 11:23.584
Yeah.

11:23.617 --> 11:24.718
No, uh‐uh, why?

11:24.751 --> 11:25.852
Well, I was thinking

11:25.886 --> 11:27.087
maybe we could
go see it.

11:27.120 --> 11:28.789
Come on, people,
the bell has rung.

11:28.822 --> 11:31.157
Quit your dilly‐dallying
and get to class!

11:31.191 --> 11:33.794
