Skips‐A‐Lot,
come on, let's go!

11:33.827 --> 11:35.195
Yes, ma'am...
I mean, sir.

11:35.228 --> 11:36.997
(LAUGHTER)

11:37.030 --> 11:38.732
I was actually...
Ohh...

11:38.765 --> 11:40.266
I was actually thinking,
um...

11:40.300 --> 11:42.235
We could hang out
at my house Friday night.

11:42.268 --> 11:45.205
My parents are going out
and my brothers aren't
going to be around.

11:45.238 --> 11:46.640
And so, I thought, um...

11:46.673 --> 11:48.008
I thought we could just
hang out or something...

11:48.041 --> 11:51.444
Come on! Come on,
get the lead out.
Let's go!

11:51.477 --> 11:52.679
So Friday night
at my house?

11:52.713 --> 11:54.548
Uhh...
Hey!

11:54.581 --> 11:55.616
Yeah.

11:55.649 --> 11:57.050
Romeo and Juliet.

11:57.083 --> 11:59.986
Come on.
Last one in class,
first one on welfare.

12:00.554 --> 12:01.755
It's your choice.

12:16.603 --> 12:18.471
I like your room, Sam.

12:18.505 --> 12:19.940
Oh, thanks.

12:20.907 --> 12:23.510
Oh, whoa! Cool sheets!

12:23.544 --> 12:26.613
(IMITATES OBI WAN)
"May the force
be with you."

12:26.647 --> 12:28.014
(FORCED LAUGH)
(BED SPRINGS CREAK)

12:28.048 --> 12:30.851
All right...
OK, let's see here.

12:30.884 --> 12:33.620
