12:39.392 --> 12:40.927
Could I borrow
your pencil?

12:40.961 --> 12:43.263
Oh, yeah. OK, yeah, sure.

12:45.431 --> 12:46.432
There you go.

13:01.648 --> 13:02.849
Here you go. Thanks.

13:03.617 --> 13:04.918
Thanks.

13:08.388 --> 13:09.856
What's the matter, Sam?

13:10.524 --> 13:12.258
Oh, nothing! Nothing.

13:13.159 --> 13:15.328
