like chips or cookies?

14:06.880 --> 14:09.916
No, I'm sorry.
My parents don't
let us eat junk food.

14:18.725 --> 14:19.926
(HUMS)

14:19.960 --> 14:22.495
Do you want to watch TV?

14:22.529 --> 14:24.164
