is on.

14:24.197 --> 14:26.032
(IMITATES
HORSHACK'S LAUGH)

14:27.534 --> 14:28.902
Are you OK?

14:28.935 --> 14:30.971
That's Horshack...
From the show.

14:32.005 --> 14:35.776
Oh. Well, I've never
really seen it before, so...

14:35.809 --> 14:37.010
What?

14:37.678 --> 14:40.013
Well, I don't
really watch TV.

14:40.046 --> 14:41.882
