I've been hogging these.

14:51.892 --> 14:53.259
(CRUNCHES)

14:56.162 --> 14:57.163
(CRUNCHES)

15:00.066 --> 15:01.802
Did you want
something to drink?

15:01.835 --> 15:02.869
Mm‐hmm.

15:02.903 --> 15:04.705
OK, I'll go get
some lemonade.

15:04.738 --> 15:06.439
(FART‐LIKE SOUND)

15:06.472 --> 15:09.475
